# SEMrush authority miner results
#
# Keep this repository raw-scrape-only for repeatable re-screening.
# Derived model outputs, chunks, clusters, and reports stay local unless they
# were already tracked before this policy changed.
semrush-authority-runs/**/*
!semrush-authority-runs/**/
!semrush-authority-runs/**/raw-rows.jsonl
!semrush-authority-runs/**/scrape-summary.json
!semrush-authority-runs/*/run-index.json
!semrush-authority-runs/*/targets*.json
!semrush-authority-runs/*/targets*.jsonl
!semrush-authority-runs/*/targets*.txt

.DS_Store
*.log
*.tmp
*.zip
*.tar
*.tar.gz
*.tgz
*.gz
*.7z

.env
.env.*
*.pem
*.key
*token*.json
*credential*.json
*credentials*.json
*cookie*.json
*secret*.json

node_modules/
.cache/
semrush-authority-runs/**/pre-*
semrush-authority-runs/**/pre-*/**
semrush-authority-runs/**/archive/
semrush-authority-runs/**/archive/**
semrush-authority-runs/**/backup/
semrush-authority-runs/**/backup/**
